<p color="yellow">Breeze::OS Installer Setup -- LVM Physical Volumes</p>
<p>
A <b>physical volume</b> (PV) can be created using any block device; but,<br>our partitioning scheme creates only one volume group <b>vg_store</b>.<br>You <b>must select</b> the partitions you wish to turn into physical volumes; you <b>may</b> also<br>associate more than one physical volume to a volume group, by assigning<br>the <b>same volume group name</b> to several physical volumes or devices.<br>You can either <b>create</b>, <b>merge</b>, or <b>ignore</b> a physical volume.
</p>
<p>
Click on <a href="action=apply"><img width="16" height="16" src="install/images/next.png"></a> to <b>Create LVM Physical Volumes</b>.<br>
Click on <a href="action=continue"><img width="16" height="16" src="install/images/next.png"></a> to <b>Continue</b>.
</p>
